This directory contains internal documentation on the weird and
wonderful workings of Intuition:

ISM.txt:
- Describes Intuition's state machine and token passing.

Locking.txt:
- Describes Intuition's locking scheme.

MenuVerify.txt:
- Description of some of the complexities of the menu-verify handling.

NativePort.txt:
- Describes the state of the native port of Intuition in V42:src/kickstart.

SunBuilding.txt:
- A bit on how to build Intuition on the Sun.

AAA.txt:
- Ideas on what needs doing for AAA
